Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And I go to Page 04 of Head MRI
And I select 'Finding' radio button

When I select 'Ischemia' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled

And 'Localization' tab is enabled and preselected
And 'Ischemia area I' tab is enabled
And 'Ischemia area II' tab is enabled
And 'Vascular occlusion' tab is enabled

When I select 'Vascular occlusion' tab
Then 'Vascular occlusion' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Vascular occlusion' checkbox
Then 'Localization*' localizer is enabled
And 'DD artifact TOF angiography' checkbox is enabled
And 'Blooming artifact' checkbox is enabled
And 'Intra-arterial FLAIR signal enhancement' checkbox is enabled
And 'Longitudinal expansion of thrombus' input field is enabled

And 'None' radio button is enabled
And 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'Moderate' radio button is enabled
And 'Pronounced' radio button is enabled

And 'Anterior communicating artery' checkbox is enabled
And 'Posterior communicating artery' checkbox is enabled

And 'Collateralization of the ICA via ECA branches' checkbox is enabled
And 'Perfusion of the ICA, pars cervicalis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Leptomeningeal collaterals' checkbox is enabled

And 'Cervical vessel elongation' checkbox is enabled
And 'High grade stenosis upstream cervical artery' checkbox is enabled
And 'Occlusion of upstream cervical artery' checkbox is enabled
And 'Thrombus in upstream cervical artery' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dissection of upstream cervical artery' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ostial stenosis affected vessel' checkbox is enabled

When I open 'Localization*' localizer
And I select 'ACA – Ant. cerebral artery'
Then 'ACA – Ant. cerebral artery', 'ACA - A1' and 'ACA - A2' options are selected
When I click on X button
Then localizer is closed

When I click on 'DD artifact TOF angiography' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Blooming artifact' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Intra-arterial FLAIR signal enhancement' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected

When I enter '1' in the 'Longitudinal expansion of thrombus' input field
Then value is accepted
When I enter '99' in the 'Longitudinal expansion of thrombus' input field
Then value is accepted

When I select 'None' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Low' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Moderate' radio button
Then radio button is selected
When I select 'Pronounced' radio button
Then radio button is selected

When I click on 'Anterior communicating artery' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Posterior communicating artery' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected

When I click on 'Collateralization of the ICA via ECA branches' checkbox
Then 'Retrograde perfusion of the ophthalmic artery' checkbox is enabled
When I click on 'Retrograde perfusion of the ophthalmic artery' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Perfusion of the ICA, pars cervicalis' checkbox
Then 'Through contralateral external carotid artery' checkbox is enabled
And 'Through ipsilateral vertebral artery' checkbox is enabled
When I click on 'Through contralateral external carotid artery' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Through ipsilateral vertebral artery' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Leptomeningeal collaterals' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected

When I click on 'Cervical vessel elongation' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'High grade stenosis upstream cervical artery' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Occlusion of upstream cervical artery' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Thrombus in upstream cervical artery' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Dissection of upstream cervical artery' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected
When I click on 'Ostial stenosis affected vessel' checkbox
Then checkbox is selected


